{"id": 542, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个脑残粉，你做过的最疯狂的事是什么？", "description": "如果爱，请深爱，花点钱。", "record_count": 3215, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145053ZYmBSLJvq4zOe6E2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-01T01:08:44Z", "options": [{"id": 14080, "content": "买起手办来，钱就不是钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213632}, {"id": 18176, "content": "铃屋什造脑残粉?头像一直是拾皂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257981}, {"id": 14081, "content": "从六年级开始喜欢他，把他的电影电视歌曲看了一遍又一遍，听了一遍又一遍，每天必须要刷一下他的新闻微博，已经持续现在六年了，我大二了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215412}, {"id": 14337, "content": "高考完以后去看了他们的演唱会，买的是最贵的票，本来突然有紧急情况去不了了，最后拼命打电话找人把事情弄好了去的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219449}, {"id": 14339, "content": "喜欢五月天，第一次看他们的演唱会从开始哭到结束，每首歌都用尽全力去唱！哭湿了半包纸巾，买了每款纪念版T恤！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210985}, {"id": 14595, "content": "想去演唱会，想买每张专辑，想见他们。哪有什么脑残只不过是信仰。他值得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223741}, {"id": 17155, "content": "真的是爱了林俊杰10年啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248427}, {"id": 14085, "content": "看见他的图片都会不自觉的笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193670}, {"id": 14086, "content": "将自己的猫手指甲保存下来！", "image": "img/option/option/201606052114434yK7NcSXCYpbnkJH.jpg", "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205981}, {"id": 14088, "content": "第一次抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205522}, {"id": 14344, "content": "为了买新款的产品通宵排队(๑>◡<๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219624}, {"id": 14345, "content": "我是王的臣民、", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219632}, {"id": 15881, "content": "去台湾就买了周杰伦小公举的专辑。。然后没钱了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238166}, {"id": 14347, "content": "我只想說 我喜歡你ㄐㄧˋㄒㄧㄣˉㄌㄧㄥˊ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219636}, {"id": 14348, "content": "泡过贴吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219644}, {"id": 16140, "content": "买了好多皮肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237086}, {"id": 44044, "content": "脑残到底", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440413}, {"id": 14093, "content": "就算对其他明星再喜欢，1个月以后也变路人了，但是他们我喜欢了8年。不过都8年了还是单身狗因为完全看不上身边的人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215535}, {"id": 14349, "content": "就是想为了他买买买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219680}, {"id": 14095, "content": "没有最疯狂，只有更疯狂", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212716}, {"id": 14607, "content": "再穷 也要面子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224013}, {"id": 14096, "content": "果粉熬夜看了近几年现场发布会，却没在第一时间入手新发布产品。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214292}, {"id": 14097, "content": "^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209728}, {"id": 14354, "content": "只要看到他的广告牌都会合影一张，代言的产品通通买回家，会把他的照片手机壁纸屏保，也会把10086设成他的名字。。。在微博会备注为老公，偶尔会做梦梦见他，在唱K的时候当成他的演唱会全唱他的歌，并且保持尖叫的兴奋状态。。。。太多了，下次想到再写( •ิ_• ิ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195503}, {"id": 14610, "content": "看见每个男的都会和他比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223980}, {"id": 14100, "content": "买了三瓶印着他头像的饮料", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215612}, {"id": 14357, "content": "为喜欢的东西正名。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219796}, {"id": 12055, "content": "花了毕生积蓄看了一场演唱会", "image": null, "praise_count": 202, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 14103, "content": "是脑残粉。想当美美的脑残粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215630}, {"id": 18967, "content": "在台北街头淅淅沥沥的小雨中站了一天为了排个签售会还开着视频准备让朋友听歌结果老萧一句没唱。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262096}, {"id": 12056, "content": "他出的手机，每一款我都买（害羞脸）", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 15897, "content": "上课一直在哼歌，作业里也写", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238309}, {"id": 14106, "content": "不觉得脑残，只是他结了婚?消息出来，会觉得自己的世界空了，得知他有了女儿，就想着连他的女儿一起爱着。?爱了16年的杰伦粉", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211056Nv6Qt9VlTsAWeBKX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215593}, {"id": 15130, "content": "每天晚上听Jay的歌睡着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231669}, {"id": 16154, "content": "我居然喜欢了一个男人，两年了，不可思议！现在发现，我比以前更爱他！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241736}, {"id": 14108, "content": "高三毕业剃了光头.....顺便说一句，我是个女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212730}, {"id": 14620, "content": "大件东西从不上网买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224159}, {"id": 14109, "content": "花了生活费的大部分买了它，却一直没怎么用过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126625}, {"id": 14877, "content": "每个月都给手机充值", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227581}, {"id": 14110, "content": "中学喜欢一个已经去世了的摇滚乐手，在家附近一个大十字路口，当时有一面墙正在粉刷，在他忌日那天我和小伙伴靠着墙摆了他照片和鲜花，还点了蜡烛。现在回想起来分分钟要被当邪教抓走的节奏。但去年出国旅游时还是放弃了去迪士尼，专门用了一天跑到海边小镇他的陵园去祭拜??。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215699}, {"id": 14366, "content": "为了她，十年不曾真心爱过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219855}, {"id": 14880, "content": "索大法好！雄起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227702}, {"id": 16163, "content": "觉得自己以前特low，现在不论多疯狂都可以接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241901}, {"id": 18467, "content": "扭秧歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259324}, {"id": 14116, "content": "等在时装秀门口，希望看他一眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215823}, {"id": 15652, "content": "看过她所有泡沫剧，5年不敢动笔画偶像^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236612}, {"id": 21284, "content": "2500生活费 买了双2200的aj", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218230}, {"id": 42277, "content": "分分钟难以停止爱比伯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429564}, {"id": 14118, "content": "他说话的时候屏气偷听", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213227}, {"id": 14630, "content": "就酱，不想错过ta的一分一秒", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211107odE2ZOIvcMgKbfFN.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224313}]}